:#*****************************************************************************
:#                                                                            *
:#  Filename:	    vcvars.bat						      *
:#                                                                            *
:#  Description:    Run vcvarsall.bat for the latest Visual C++ installed     *
:#                                                                            *
:#  Usage:	    Run this script with option -? to display a help screen.  *
:#                                                                            *
:#  Notes:								      *
:#									      *
:#  History:                                                                  *
